      <h2 class="h1-seo-replace my-5">Accommodation Information for Students</h2>
      <h4>General Policy</h4>
      <br />
      <p class="lead mb-4 text-justify">
        Please note that all multi-day sailing courses (except Start Yachting
        course) can include accommodation on the training boat for students but
        you need to confirm your intentions and book the cleaning & bedding
        service for 20 euro/person in advance.
      </p>
      <p class="lead mb-4 text-justify">
        In addition, our friends between them operate a fleet of licensed yachts
        within the Grand Harbour marinas with accommodation options based on the
        AirBnB basis.
      </p>
      <p class="lead mb-4 text-justify">
        This option may make your, and your non sailing family’s stay even more
        enjoyable and convenient. Why stay at a hotel when you can experience
        life as a live-aboard?
      </p>
      <p class="lead mb-4 text-justify">
        If you prefer a hotel, we can recommend some in the near environs. The
        transport from Malta Airport to our marina usually take around 15
        minutes by taxi.
      </p>
